text: Josep Tarradellas i Joan (), 1st Marquess of Tarradellas (1899 in Cervelló, Baix Llobregat – 1988 in Barcelona) was a Spanish politician. He was President of Catalonia from 1954 to 1980. ==References== Category:1899 births Category:1988 deaths Category:Presidents of the Government of Catalonia
title: Josep Tarradellas
